parameters.name: R6A_FLUX
parameters.description: Flux measured in HET energy channel R6A (1.8-3.2 MeV electrons). The coincidence logic for this channel is A1.^A2.B.^C1.

parameters.name: R6B_FLUX

parameters.name: R7A_FLUX
